  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    ‘On hold’ health claims on foods if there’s a no-deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    How to use ‘on hold’ health claims that are still under consideration in the EU in the UK, if there's a no-deal Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

